{"tid":1604870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［主線］聽日一定要做啲有標誌性嘅","createTime":"2019-09-30T05:57:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T19:33:31.000Z","uid":150267,"like":122,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":94,"replies":[{"pid":"eac738986931cc2188d07fb74cea7d2f17f75bb4","tid":1604870,"uid":150267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:57:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">3點人人燒黨旗<br />\nIf We Burn, You Burn With Us</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點解係三點?</span></span></strong><br />\n參考手足個post<br />\n<br />\n毛澤東在1949.10.1下午3時宣布<br />\n「同胞們，中華人民共和國中央人民政府今天成立了！」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2019年10月1日北京時間下午3時正<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1604498\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1604498</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有咩要準備？</span></span></strong><br />\n有旗帶旗 <br />\n無既今日即刻print a4又好a3又好 個個一齊大細都無所謂<br />\nBtw依樣係和理非可以做既野-print多啲派俾手足又好自己燒多啲又好<br />\n火機/火柴<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">點樣燒？</span></strong></span><br />\n自己燒又得<br />\n多人一齊燒有個火堆 一齊扔落去慢慢燒都得<br />\n（最緊要有人傳媒影到 當然大家要black bloc)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AXr3HtN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAXr3HtN.jpg&h=bf4d7167&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外<br />\n［整合］十一執齊野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1603888\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1603888</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n幫推<br />\n[觀念]出去嘅人要明白嘅事<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1603908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1603908</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <br />\n<br />\n十一國殤　六區開花<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1600404\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1600404</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d6ebc2cd8a69c6f0699c4aff2fb80fea64c1d731","tid":1604870,"uid":118688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:58:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"78406b5b28d99e5b134f3ca4726c84e61eb40535","tid":1604870,"uid":311486,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:58:47.000Z","msg":"今晚需要一個集氣大會。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1604777\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1604777</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"05d279df7deb3cd51abcd27d7e7e664e3eed0585","tid":1604870,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:58:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1457781aa4e14dceed21526e080df3ec8e4953a3","tid":1604870,"uid":194298,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:00:28.000Z","msg":"邊度拉支黨旗返黎???<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都知難架喇，所以我會印定一千張A3彩PRINT到時派，有拎到係手既唔好亂咁揮，支旗係要黎燒的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e5b89780263aa80c004f53fb000e1e874a27fa8","tid":1604870,"uid":134054,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:00:45.000Z","msg":"贊成 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">10月1日手足要黑衫攝衫<br />\n一人一支漂白水反攻<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一人一個鎖 狗鐵一封站就反鎖狗入面<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">要比多啲人睇到<br />\n10月1號熄燈嘅時候<br />\n係去Twitter<br />\n#LIHKG101<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n快啲幫手share<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"221629123253e42119020967c2de0f209ac8f9c7","tid":1604870,"uid":224869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:03:38.000Z","msg":"徵哨<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/pigeonpatrol\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fpigeonpatrol&d=eFPPjfgCRb